### COMMENTS
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Create comment (authenticated)
POST {{baseUrl}}/comments
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "invoice_id": "{{invoiceId}}",
  "comment_text": "I love this, we can pay now"
}

